Usage: addEndCap [-help] [-area <box>] [-coreBoundaryOnly]
                 [-powerDomain <name>] [-prefix <prefix>]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-area <box>                # Area in which endcaps are to be inserted
                           # (box, optional)
-coreBoundaryOnly          # Places endcaps only at the core-boundary and not
                           # abutting obstructions (bool, optional)
-powerDomain <name>        # Power domain for which endcaps are to be inserted
                           # (string, optional)
-prefix <prefix>           # Prefix of endcaps to inserted (string, optional)